    {
      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 139  to annually transfer 80% of the sales and use taxes, interest, and penalties collected during the preceding fiscal year from sporting goods retailers from the general fund to the Kentucky Heritage Land Conservation fund."
    }
